:0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>敢做不敢認</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你識佢？</blockquote><br />\nSure</blockquote><br />\n其實我識得你<br />\n你老母俾狗屌架嘛"},{"pid":"8ac13bcb888c315830a70ae7a2490ec58ab250e7","tid":262192,"uid":25999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>敢做不敢認</blockquote><br />\n屌您老母，你係現場咩？"},{"pid":"64de191c1318ed55f827780f4d30a104431a21dd","tid":262192,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>敢做不敢認</blockquote><br />\n傻的嗎？同黨？"},{"pid":"86f2105d43b869bc541af745c4b9172bc174dfdd","tid":262192,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>敢做不敢認</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmark"},{"pid":"349d977a9a63fccbbb4b6cb5e3d8ab90ec3213d0","tid":262192,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>敢做不敢認</blockquote><br />\n屌您老母，你係現場咩？</blockquote><br />\n咁清楚<br />\n唔通佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c4dc2b482a1e73330d8be02acc86afb5b163d0","tid":262192,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>敢做不敢認</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你識佢？</blockquote><br />\nSure</blockquote><br />\n你係現場？"},{"pid":"f7ba0582d7ccfd9a85df0b092d79b938623f3370","tid":262192,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>敢做不敢認</blockquote><br />\nblocked"},{"pid":"c5b358f8d2ed5b59a931802d5aacedfb3883aa1a","tid":262192,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:31:10.000Z","msg":"唔好咁撚仆街啦屈鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多個人落案會升職咩"},{"pid":"845111fb4f36e489472231c0b6e306c03016f3b3","tid":262192,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T20:46:39.000Z","msg":"拉曬班仆街去坐監啦 咁鍾意搞事"},{"pid":"e234ceb4c4c86811022275dcd2097676618aa6a7","tid":262192,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T21:15:01.000Z","msg":"正常香港人係打<br />\n敢做唔敢認<br />\n打得敢做不敢認<br />\n係乜嘢人大家心知肚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60d7fcf35ed9ffeb139b0b789c0e73bc4cc91b8","tid":262192,"uid":31368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T21:39:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉曬班仆街去坐監啦 咁鍾意搞事</blockquote><br />\n拍攝都唔得？拉撚曬記者囉？無腦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2e7351bcf30620639ed79a5a282f4cfb0792d9","tid":262192,"uid":54256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T22:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉曬班仆街去坐監啦 咁鍾意搞事</blockquote><br />\n我立即屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c34bbd95b068458ae928f2dc100620c3b727de4","tid":262192,"uid":50533,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T22:54:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}